# | Plot Type     | Data Type Shown      | Purpose in ML                          | Differs From                      |
# | ------------- | -------------------- | -------------------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
# | **Line Plot** | Continuous over time | Track training metrics (loss/accuracy) | Unlike scatter → shows trend      |
# | **Scatter**   | Two numeric features | See correlation, clusters              | Unlike line → no trend line       |
# | **Histogram** | Single feature dist. | Check data distribution                | Unlike bar → for continuous data  |
# | **Bar Chart** | Categories + values  | Compare feature importance, models     | Unlike histogram → for categories |
# | **Subplots**  | Multiple plots       | Compare side by side                   | Organizing tool, not unique chart |
